0. Bundle install
1. Check if Unicorn is installed => str =  `gem list` [then look for unicorn]
	a. Install Unicorn. `gem install unicorn`
2. Set-up unicorn.rb `pwd`
3. Make sure Nginx is installed => which nginx
	a. Install Nginx => apt get install nginx
	b. Get rid of the bad shit (of Nginx) => delete /etc/nginx/conf.d/defaults /etc/nginx/sites [sudo rm /path/to/directory/ *]
	c. Add our shit to Nginx
4. Update Nginx for new Unicorn
5. Boot up Unicorns
6. Restart Nginx
7. Have a snack and take a nap

